data.title: 2003) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Speedy West - was born Wesley Webb West, January 25th, 1925 at Springfield, Missouri.   He was raised 10 miles east of Springfield on a farm where he grew up learning all about farm life and dairy farming. His family were musically inclined and he decided he wanted to learn to play the steel guitar at an early age....
